Bank Danamon seeks approvals for deals . Indonesian large privately - owned PT Bank Danamon Indonesia said on Wednesday it planned to hold an extraordinary shareholders meeting in late August to seek approvals for proposed transactions with subsidiaries . Danamon said in an announcement that on July 25 the bank had signed memorandum of understandings with several subsidiaries to provide support services including property , advertising , telecommunications and transportation to the bank . The bank said the deals would increase efficiency and maximise the firm ' s financial capibility in the face of rising competition in the banking sector . - - Jakarta newsroom + 6221 384 - 6364 
